G'MIC, the GREYC's Magic Image Converter, an open and full-featured
framework mage processing, providing several different user interfaces
to convert/manipulate/filter/visualize generic image datasets, from 1d
scalar signals to 3d+t sequences of multi-spectral volumetric images.

gimp-gmic-plugin: The gmic_gimp plig-in brings the G'MIC capabilities
to the GIMP image retouching software.

http://gmic.sourceforge.net/gimp.shtml